
Overview of noun ninja

The noun ninja has 2 senses (no senses from tagged texts)
                                        
1. ninja -- (a member of the ninja who were trained in martial arts and hired for espionage or sabotage or assassinations; a person skilled in ninjutsu)
2. ninja -- (a class of 14th century Japanese who were trained in martial arts and were hired for espionage and assassinations)
